Third-party assets and trademarks:

The "Clawd" character and its likeness are the property of Anthropic, PBC. The
Clawd animation pack in `data/clawd/` and the preview clips in `assets/` are
NOT part of the MIT-licensed Software above and are NOT licensed under MIT.
All rights to the character are reserved by Anthropic, PBC.

  * This is an unofficial fan project. It is not affiliated with, sponsored by,
    or endorsed by Anthropic.
  * The pixel-art sprite renditions are adapted from
    https://github.com/rullerzhou-afk/clawd-on-desk. That project's source code
    is licensed AGPL-3.0, but its artwork/theme assets are explicitly "NOT
    covered by AGPL-3.0; all rights reserved by copyright holders" — consistent
    with the Clawd character being Anthropic's intellectual property.
  * The art is bundled here only for personal, non-commercial maker use, the
    same way the upstream community projects bundle it.

If you fork or redistribute this repository, note that the MIT grant covers the
firmware and tooling ONLY. Replace `data/clawd/` and `assets/` with your own
art to redistribute the whole thing freely (the character system reads any
black-background GIF pack — see the README).
